    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300160571_8_1695-1758",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1695-1758",
      "markText": "符寿昭不管军务，还醉心捞钱，不过他捞钱的方式跟一般的贪官不一样，不是收受贿赂直接捞钱，而是进军“高端制造业”，自己下场赚大钱。",
      "totalCount": 1521,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300160571&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1695&rangeEnd=1758",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1732b20813aba539g0115ea?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1695&rangeEnd=1758"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300160571_19_6208-6248",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "6208-6248",
      "markText": "庆历五年，担任御史的何郯力证石介诈死之说不可信，并直言夏竦就是奸臣。",
      "totalCount": 1521,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300160571&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=6208&rangeEnd=6248",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1732b20813aba539g0115ea?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=6208&rangeEnd=6248"
    },
    {
